sys_pd_lane.description: This is the preselection of candidates phase
sys_pd_lane.label: Preselection
sys_pd_lane.name: preselection

sys_pd_activity.description: If the candidates are correctly scored change their state to preselected
sys_pd_activity.label: Candidates Preselection Scored
sys_pd_activity.name: show_list_of_records

sys_pd_activity.description: Define for each candidate if they are Eligible or not eligible. Clicking on the Name of the candidate you should be able to find their CV. If not eligible please open the candidate and select the relative exclusion reasons
sys_pd_activity.label: Candidates Eligibility
sys_pd_activity.name: show_list_of_records

sys_pd_activity.description: A new HR Case has been assigned to you, please go to HR Agent workspace to preview and generate the Preselection Report for this assessment
sys_pd_activity.label: Open the relative HR Case to generate the Preselection report
sys_pd_activity.name: show_list_of_records

sys_pd_activity.description: If the candidates are correctly scored change their state to selected
sys_pd_activity.label: Candidates Selection Scored
sys_pd_activity.name: show_list_of_records

sys_pd_activity.description: Score each assessment selection criteria opening each record and looking at the candidate answers
sys_pd_activity.label: Score Preselection Criteria
sys_pd_activity.name: show_list_of_records_1

sys_pd_activity.description: If the candidate screening is terminated please change the assessment state selection
sys_pd_activity.label: End Preselection CBT phase
sys_pd_activity.name: user_form

sys_pd_activity.description: Here you can amend the preselection criteria and relative questions for this specific assessment. Click on Open List if you wish to add more
sys_pd_activity.label: Amend Selection Criteria
sys_pd_activity.name: show_list_of_records_2

sys_pd_activity.label: Create HR Case to generate PDF
sys_pd_activity.name: automated_create_record

sys_pd_activity.description: If no candidate is still on pending you are ready to move to the next phase of the process
sys_pd_activity.label: End Eligibility phase
sys_pd_activity.name: user_form

sys_pd_activity.description: Please approve or reject the score proposed for each candidate
sys_pd_activity.label: Candidate Selection Approval
sys_pd_activity.name: show_list_of_records_2

sys_pd_activity.description: Please confirm the preselection scores are accurately calculated by Prometric for the Computer base tests.
sys_pd_activity.label: Candidates Preselection CBT
sys_pd_activity.name: show_list_of_records

sys_pd_activity.description: Here you can amend the preselection criteria and relative questions for this specific assessment. Click on Preselection Criteria Tab if you wish to add / delete
sys_pd_activity.label: Amend Preselection Criteria
sys_pd_activity.name: show_list_of_records_4

sys_pd_activity.description: If the candidate assessment is terminated please change the assessment state to reserve list
sys_pd_activity.label: End Selection phase
sys_pd_activity.name: user_form

sys_pd_activity.description: Here is the list of candidate for the vacancy. You can move to closure when all the candidate have terminated their assessment process (State = Closure)
sys_pd_activity.label: Waiting for all the Candidates to be assessed
sys_pd_activity.name: show_list_of_records

sys_pd_activity.description: If no more changes are needed for assessment you are ready to move to the next phase of the process
sys_pd_activity.label: Publication Ready
sys_pd_activity.name: user_form_1

sys_pd_activity.description: The publication was published, please provide all the information needed for the assessment process that should automatically start once the publication expires
sys_pd_activity.label: Fill President & Rapporteur
sys_pd_activity.name: user_form

sys_pd_activity.description: Here you can amend the exclusion reasons for the this specific assessment. Click on Exclusion Reasons Tab if you wish to add / delete
sys_pd_activity.label: Amend Exclusion Reason
sys_pd_activity.name: show_list_of_records_3

sys_pd_activity.description: If the candidate screening is terminated please change the assessment state selection
sys_pd_activity.label: End Preselection phase
sys_pd_activity.name: user_form

sys_pd_activity.description: Score each assessment selection criteria opening each record and looking at the candidate answers
sys_pd_activity.label: Score Selection Criteria
sys_pd_activity.name: show_list_of_records_1
